{"tid":32891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AKB48上海騷遭反日人士抗議 粉絲搶國旗丟","createTime":"2016-12-10T12:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T14:11:19.000Z","uid":7033,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7439c7f7dfc9b69243b030f0b1d231bf610a9ba","tid":32891,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"日本女子偶像組合AKB48派出三名成員渡邊麻友、川本紗矢同伊豆田莉奈現身上海舉行嘅活動，宣佈組合嚟緊喺中國嘅發展大計。<br />\n<br />\n現場除咗唔少AKB嘅國內粉絲，仲有一班愛國人士踩場，佢哋手執「萬眾一心 愛我中華 抵制日韓」嘅字句，仲有人拎住AKB同日本首相安倍晉三嘅合照，以及AKB為日本自衞隊拍攝嘅宣傳海報。現場嘅抗議人士話，「一二．九」抗日救亡運動紀念日啱啱過咗，南京大屠殺紀念日又即將來臨，偏偏喺呢個時候有對中日關係有負面影響嘅偶像團體嚟到大陸，「實在令人難以接受」。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指，一眾反日抗議人士令在現嘅AKB支持者非常不滿，fans激動得扯下橫額，兼用日語罵爆，更將抗議者手中嘅大陸國旗丟入垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56030135&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56030135%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161210&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2FwZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3817dd32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56030135%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161210&h=6cc59fa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56030135&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161210</a>"},{"pid":"6f370b75e92507552f0c621d1bab5be299edd897","tid":32891,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0a639b2905db1fc619876d70e81d63e18300c4f","tid":32891,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"上海隊野係咪無咗？"},{"pid":"bc96f607f77525bdd76570636b3999a01899015a","tid":32891,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗 好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f20